Class EmailPane

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.Parent

            • javafx.scene.layout.GridPane
              • q5.EmailPane

  • public class EmailPane
extends javafx.scene.layout.GridPane

    EmailPane represents an email with text fields for receiver, cc, bcc, subject, and content of the email. There is also a button to print out its contents.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
